org.opencypher.gremlin.translation

Interface GremlinSteps<T,P>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - translation target type
    P - predicate target type
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BytecodeGremlinSteps, GroovyGremlinSteps, TraversalGremlinSteps

    public interface GremlinSteps<T,P>
    Gremlin GraphTraversal DSL wrapper. For DSL details, see Graph Traversal Steps.

    Implementations define a translation target that can be built with GraphTraversal steps.

    Note: steps are expected to be side-effecting, thus, unsuitable for use in immutable contexts.

    See Also:
    Translator
